20:22.060 --> 20:23.820
- You didn't know about this until just now?
- No...

20:24.010 --> 20:26.480
- No, I'm sorry...
- Kitty, this is breaking news.

20:26.650 --> 20:28.710
It's... it's everywhere. And I...

20:29.070 --> 20:30.370
you knew what I was going through today.

20:30.550 --> 20:32.520
