has a few problems of her own.

21:21.290 --> 21:22.240
What do you mean?

21:22.390 --> 21:23.160
She had an affair.

21:23.280 --> 21:24.860
I saw it online.

21:24.980 --> 21:25.650
Really.

21:26.460 --> 21:28.110
Wait, how do I know this and you don't?

21:28.230 --> 21:29.700
Well, no. I... I heard the rumors.

21:29.820 --> 21:31.410
I just wasn't sure if they were true.

21:31.540 --> 21:34.660
