22:48.240 --> 22:49.980
- Kevin!
- Kevin!

22:50.910 --> 22:51.800
Unbelievable.

22:51.920 --> 22:53.210
- Well, I could take you home.
- No, it's okay.

22:53.370 --> 22:55.060
You have Evan. I'll...

22:55.280 --> 22:56.720
I'll take a cab.

